===Transitive verb===
'''to chase''' (chasing, chased, chased)

#<!--VTrPursue-->To [[pursue]], to [[follow]] at [[speed]].
#<!--VTrHunt-->To hunt.
#<!--VTrCricket-->{{cricket}} To [[attempt]] to [[win]] by scoring the required number of runs in the final [[innings]].
#{{baseball}} To swing at a [[pitch]] outside of the [[strike zone]], typically an outside pitch
#: ''Jones '''chases''' one out of the [[zone]] for strike two.''
#{{baseball}} To produce enough [[offense]] to cause the [[pitcher]] to be removed
#: ''The rally '''chased''' the starter.''

